word: G3364 - οὐ μή - ou mḗ - oo may - Any more

sections.paragraph: not at all, anymore, at all, by no means, by any means, neither, never, in no case, nor ever

ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: That is, G3756 and G3361; a double negative strengthening the denial; not at all: - any more, at all, by any (no) means, neither, never, no (at all), in no case (wise), nor ever, not (at all, in any wise). Compare G3378.
